comment: [Observable in enhanced video] Curry (GSW) moves his pivot foot.
DeRozan (TOR) leads with his knee as part of a natural shooting motion and the contact is not delivered to Green (GSW).
Barnes (GSW) makes contact with Joseph (TOR) after he secures the loose ball.
Barnes (GSW) dislodges Lowry (TOR) and affects his ability to retrieve the rebound.
As Curry (GSW) splits the double team, Scola (TOR) extends his leg and trips him.
Green (GSW) jumps vertically and absorbs the contact as he legally contests DeRozan's (TOR) driving layup attempt.
Lowry (TOR) is retreating and maintains legal guarding position as he defends Curry's (GSW) drive to the basket. He cleanly blocks the shot attempt.
RHH shows Barnes (GSW) and Joseph (TOR) both have their hands on the ball and Barnes is not dislodged while attempting to secure possession and pass to a teammate.
Lowry (TOR) grabs Iguodala's (GSW) right arm and affects his ability to defend.
Lowry (TOR) clamps Iguodala's (GSW) left arm as he sets the screen and affects his ability to defend.
Scola (TOR) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).

Green (GSW) jumps vertically and maintains legal guarding position as he absorbs the contact from Lowry (TOR) on the drive to the basket. When Green's arms come down he cleanly blocks the shot attempt.
After Green (GSW) secures the rebound, Lowry (TOR) pushes him and forces him to fall OOB.
Lowry (TOR) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).
